# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __iter__, __next__, __len__ across all 3 re subjects
#
# 3 classes x 3 methods = 9 rows.
# All nine values are false. re.Match defines __getitem__ (wave 677, true)
# for subscript group access but does NOT define __iter__, __next__, or
# __len__ in its own __dict__. re.Pattern and re.RegexFlag are false for
# all three methods.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

